title: Fighting False News in Ukraine, Facebook Fact Checkers Tread a Blurry Line
text: Facebook hired a Ukrainian group battling Russian disinformation to flag misleading posts. But critics say the fact checkers’ work veers into activism.

title: Earnings Watch: Big Tech’s big test arrives in the busiest week of earnings season
text: Even though Big Tech’s day in the antitrust spotlight is delayed, the coming week will be a big test for the biggest names on Wall Street.

title: Biden's path to the White House could hit a dead end on Facebook
text: Mark Zuckerberg’s autocratic nature and fear of anti-trust legislation might see him plump for Trump in the race for president
